<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Business English – Useful Language</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --cream: #f7f4ef;
    --cream-dark: #ede9e1;
    --ink: #1a1714;
    --ink-mid: #4a4540;
    --ink-light: #8a857e;
    --gold: #b8860b;
    --gold-light: #f5e8c0;
    --gold-mid: #e8c84a;
    --teal: #1a5c52;
    --teal-light: #d6ece8;
    --red: #8b1a1a;
    --red-light: #f5dada;
    --blue: #1a3a5c;
    --blue-light: #d6e4f0;
    --border: rgba(26,23,20,0.12);
    --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,23,20,0.08);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* ── TOP NAV ── */
  .topbar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #f7f4ef;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 56px;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .topbar-brand {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .topbar-brand span { color: var(--gold-mid); }
  .search-wrap {
    position: relative;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 380px;
  }
  .search-wrap input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 7px 14px 7px 36px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: none;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: #f7f4ef;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    outline: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .search-wrap input::placeholder { color: rgba(247,244,239,0.45); }
  .search-wrap input:focus { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
  .search-icon {
    position: absolute;
    left: 11px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .mode-btns { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .mode-btn {
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(247,244,239,0.7);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .mode-btn.active, .mode-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: #f7f4ef;
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }
  .mode-btn.active {
    background: var(--gold);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .layout { display: flex; flex: 1; }

  /* ── SIDEBAR ── */
  .sidebar {
    width: 220px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--cream-dark);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 56px;
    height: calc(100vh - 56px);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .sidebar-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .sidebar-label:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .nav-item {
    display: block;
    padding: 9px 1.25rem;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-left: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: none;
    border-right: none;
    border-top: none;
    border-bottom: none;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  .nav-item:hover { color: var(--ink); background: rgba(26,23,20,0.04); }
  .nav-item.active { color: var(--ink); border-left-color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; background: rgba(184,134,11,0.07); }
  .nav-item .unit-num {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 18px;
    background: var(--gold-light);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 18px;
    margin-right: 7px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  main {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 4rem;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  /* BROWSE MODE */
  .unit-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .unit-section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .unit-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .unit-num-badge {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .unit-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .phrase-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(340px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .phrase-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .phrase-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .phrase-card-title {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .phrase-card-title::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 10px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .phrase-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .phrase-item {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.55;
    padding: 5px 8px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .phrase-item:hover {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    color: var(--ink);
    border-color: rgba(184,134,11,0.2);
  }
  .phrase-item.highlighted {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* SEARCH RESULTS */
  #search-results { display: none; }
  .search-result-item {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
  }
  .search-result-item:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .search-result-phrase { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .search-result-phrase mark { background: var(--gold-mid); color: var(--ink); border-radius: 2px; padding: 0 2px; }
  .search-result-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-light); }
  .no-results { color: var(--ink-light); font-size: 14px; padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; }

  /* FLASHCARD MODE */
  #flashcard-mode { display: none; }
  .fc-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .fc-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
  .fc-progress-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .fc-progress-bar {
    width: 180px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fc-progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }
  .fc-progress-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-light); }

  .fc-unit-select {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .fc-unit-btn {
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .fc-unit-btn:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); }
  .fc-unit-btn.active { background: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

  .fc-card-area {
    perspective: 1000px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .fc-card-inner {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 240px;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
    border-radius: 14px;
  }
  .fc-card-inner.flipped { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .fc-face {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    min-height: 240px;
  }
  .fc-front {
    background: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .fc-back {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.3);
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }
  .fc-face-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .fc-front .fc-face-label { color: #f7f4ef; }
  .fc-back .fc-face-label { color: var(--gold); }
  .fc-phrase {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .fc-front .fc-phrase { color: #f7f4ef; }
  .fc-back .fc-phrase { color: var(--ink); }
  .fc-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .fc-front .fc-sub { color: #f7f4ef; }
  .fc-back .fc-sub { color: var(--ink-mid); }
  .fc-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    opacity: 0.35;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .fc-front .fc-hint { color: #f7f4ef; }
  .fc-back .fc-hint { color: var(--ink); }

  .fc-controls {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .fc-nav { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .fc-btn {
    padding: 9px 22px;
    border-radius: 7px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .fc-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--cream-dark); border-color: var(--ink-mid); }
  .fc-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.3; cursor: not-allowed; }
  .fc-btn.primary { background: var(--ink); color: #f7f4ef; border-color: var(--ink); }
  .fc-btn.primary:hover { background: var(--ink-mid); }
  .fc-shuffle {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .fc-shuffle:hover { color: var(--ink); }

  /* QUIZ MODE */
  #quiz-mode { display: none; }
  .quiz-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .quiz-header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .quiz-header p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-light); }
  .quiz-unit-select {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .q-progress {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .q-bar { flex: 1; height: 4px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
  .q-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--teal); border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.4s; }
  .q-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-light); white-space: nowrap; }
  .q-score-badge {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--teal);
    background: var(--teal-light);
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .q-question {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-light);
  }
  .q-question .q-unit-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    background: var(--gold-light);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .q-question .q-phrase {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .q-options { display: grid; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .q-opt {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 13px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    text-align: left;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .q-opt:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); background: var(--gold-light); }
  .q-opt:disabled { cursor: default; }
  .q-opt.correct { border-color: var(--teal); background: var(--teal-light); color: var(--teal); font-weight: 500; }
  .q-opt.wrong { border-color: var(--red); background: var(--red-light); color: var(--red); }
  .q-opt .opt-letter {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .q-next-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }

  .q-done {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
  }
  .q-done-score { font-size: 64px; font-weight: 300; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1; }
  .q-done-total { font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .q-done-label { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-mid); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .q-done-bar { width: 200px; height: 8px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; overflow: hidden; }
  .q-done-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }

  .hidden { display: none !important; }

  /* Scrollbar */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .sidebar { display: none; }
    main { padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem; }
    .topbar { padding: 0 1rem; }
    .topbar-brand { font-size: 15px; }
    .phrase-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-brand">Business <span>English</span></div>
  <div class="search-wrap">
    <svg class="search-icon" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
    <input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="Phrase suchen …" oninput="handleSearch(this.value)">
  </div>
  <div class="mode-btns">
    <button class="mode-btn active" onclick="setMode('browse')">Übersicht</button>
    <button class="mode-btn" onclick="setMode('flashcard')">Karten</button>
    <button class="mode-btn" onclick="setMode('quiz')">Quiz</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="layout">
  <aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-label">Einheiten</div>
    <button class="nav-item active" onclick="scrollToUnit('u1')"><span class="unit-num">1</span>Opinions &amp; Meetings</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u2')"><span class="unit-num">2</span>Travel</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u3')"><span class="unit-num">3</span>Change</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u4')"><span class="unit-num">4</span>Organization</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u5')"><span class="unit-num">5</span>Advertising</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u6')"><span class="unit-num">6</span>Money</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u8')"><span class="unit-num">8</span>Human Resources</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u9')"><span class="unit-num">9</span>Int. Markets</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u10')"><span class="unit-num">10</span>Ethics</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u11')"><span class="unit-num">11</span>Leadership</button>
    <button class="nav-item" onclick="scrollToUnit('u12')"><span class="unit-num">12</span>Competition</button>
  </aside>

  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- SEARCH RESULTS -->
    <div id="search-results"></div>

    <!-- BROWSE MODE -->
    <div id="browse-mode">

      <div class="unit-section" id="u1">
        <div class="unit-header">
          <span class="unit-num-badge">Unit 1</span>
          <h2 class="unit-title">Opinions &amp; Meetings</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="phrase-grid">
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Asking for Opinions</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">How do you feel about that?</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">What do you think?</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">What's your view?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Giving Opinions</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">I think / I don't think that's a good idea.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">In my opinion, we need new products.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Agreeing</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">That's true.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">I agree.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Absolutely.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Exactly.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">I think so, too.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Disagreeing</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">I see / know what you mean, but I think there's a problem.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">I'm not so sure.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Maybe, but that's not enough.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Making Suggestions</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">I think we should reduce our prices.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">How about a special promotion?</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Why don't we talk to the big stores?</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Maybe / Perhaps we could offer incentives.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="unit-section" id="u2">
        <div class="unit-header">
          <span class="unit-num-badge">Unit 2</span>
          <h2 class="unit-title">Travel</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="phrase-grid">
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Answering the Phone</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Hello, Carla Rodríguez speaking.</li>
              <li class="phrase-item" onclick="toggleHighlight(this)">Good morning, Tiger Ltd.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="phrase-card">
            <div class="phrase-card-title">Making Contact</div>
            <ul class="phrase-list">
